#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.30:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Micchattavagga"
msgstr "3. The Wrong Way"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 30. Uttiyasutta → uttiya or uttika (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Uttiyasutta"
msgstr "30. With Uttiya"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.30:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā uttiyo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno "
"kho āyasmā uttiyo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Uttiya went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.3"
msgid ""
"“idha mayhaṃ, bhante, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko "
"udapādi:"
msgstr "“Just now, sir, as I was in private retreat this thought came to mind."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.4"
msgid "‘pañca kāmaguṇā vuttā bhagavatā."
msgstr "‘The Buddha has spoken of the five kinds of sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.5"
msgid "Katame nu kho pañca kāmaguṇā vuttā bhagavatā’”ti?"
msgstr "What are they?’”"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.6"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, uttiya."
msgstr "“Good, good, Uttiya!"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.7"
msgid "Pañcime kho, uttiya, kāmaguṇā vuttā mayā."
msgstr "I have spoken of these five kinds of sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.8"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.9"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā, "
msgstr ""
"Sights known by the eye that are likable, desirable, agreeable, pleasant, "
"sensual, and arousing. "

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.10"
msgid "sotaviññeyyā saddā … pe …"
msgstr "Sounds known by the ear …"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.11"
msgid "ghānaviññeyyā gandhā … pe …"
msgstr "Smells known by the nose …"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.12"
msgid "jivhāviññeyyā rasā … pe …"
msgstr "Tastes known by the tongue …"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.13"
msgid ""
"kāyaviññeyyā phoṭṭhabbā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā piyarūpā kāmūpasaṃhitā rajanīyā—"
msgstr ""
"Touches known by the body that are likable, desirable, agreeable, pleasant, "
"sensual, and arousing."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.14"
msgid "ime kho, uttiya, pañca kāmaguṇā vuttā mayā."
msgstr "These are the five kinds of sensual stimulation that I’ve spoken of."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.15"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, uttiya, pañcannaṃ kāmaguṇānaṃ pahānāya ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo "
"bhāvetabbo."
msgstr ""
"The noble eightfold path should be developed to give up these five kinds of "
"sensual stimulation."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.16"
msgid "Katamo ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo?"
msgstr "What is the noble eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.17"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"It is right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right "
"livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.30:1.18"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, uttiya, pañcannaṃ kāmaguṇānaṃ pahānāya ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko "
"maggo bhāvetabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the noble eightfold path that should be developed to give up these "
"five kinds of sensual stimulation.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.30:1.19"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.30:1.20"
msgid "Micchattavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.30:2.1"
msgid "Micchattaṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.30:2.2"
msgid "Duve paṭipadāpi ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.30:2.3"
msgid "Asappurisena dve kumbho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.30:2.4"
msgid "Samādhi vedanuttiyenāti."
msgstr ""
